name: I am a Fish
description:
You are the one who survived the space crash.
You thought you were alone.

Made for the 19th Mini Jam with ct.js game editor.

Music by Whatfunk

Genres combined: Platformer + Tech demo XD
It was supposed to be a Platformer + Shooter/BulletHell + Puzzle, but I focused too much on developing new features for my editor.
